### Register
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Owner",
  "email": "owner@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### List my workspaces (requires auth cookie)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/workspaces

### Create workspace
POST http://localhost:3000/api/workspaces
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Workspace"
}

### Manual review import
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/import
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspaceId": "WORKSPACE_ID",
  "locationId": "LOCATION_ID",
  "source": "GOOGLE",
  "authorName": "Jane D.",
  "rating": 4,
  "text": "Great service and quick support.",
  "reviewDate": "2026-02-18T00:00:00.000Z",
  "reviewUrl": "https://example.com/review/123"
}

### Generate AI draft reply
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspaceId": "WORKSPACE_ID",
  "reviewId": "REVIEW_ID",
  "provider": "openai",
  "length": "medium",
  "targetLanguage": "English",
  "escalation": true
}

### Suggest tags + sentiment
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/REVIEW_ID/suggest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspaceId": "WORKSPACE_ID",
  "provider": "openai"
}

### Approve draft reply (admin/owner)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/REVIEW_ID/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspaceId": "WORKSPACE_ID",
  "approvedReply": "Thanks for the feedback..."
}

### Export CSV (Agency)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/workspaces/WORKSPACE_ID/exports/csv?ids=REVIEW_ID_1,REVIEW_ID_2

### Stripe checkout
POST http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions/stripe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspaceId": "WORKSPACE_ID",
  "action": "checkout",
  "plan": "PRO"
}

### PayPal checkout
POST http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions/paypal
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspaceId": "WORKSPACE_ID",
  "plan": "AGENCY"
}
